trailingComments.value:
*
 *  书籍封面页点击“购买全本”：通知客户端开始购买
 *
 *  支持平台：书旗Android、书旗iOS
 *
 *  @param {int} type: 1，全本购买
 *  @param {int} payMode: 0,1,2,3 付费类型
 *  @param {String} bookId：书籍Id
 *  @param {String} bookName：书名
 *  @param {float} price：价格
 *
 *  @return 0：传入参数解析失败 1：传入参数解析成功
 *
 *  @example
 *  libSQ.exec('call-app-buy-book', {
 *   params: {
 *     type: 1,
 *     payMode: 3,
 *     bookId: '4994657',
 *     bookName: '超级苗医',
 *     price: 0.5,
 *     imgUrl: 'http://img-tailor.11222.cn/bcv/big/201706201738443950.jpg',
 *   },
 * }).then((info) => {
 *   console.log(`[call-app-buy-book][then] ${JSON.stringify(info, null, 2)}`);
 * }).catch((err) => {
 *   alert(`[call-app-buy-book][error] ${JSON.stringify(err, null, 2)}`);
 * });
